Skribisto

v 1.8.2
    First usable release. Lacks a lot of features
    New features:
    - Open/Save/Backup/autosave of notes and sheets.
    - Open multiple projects
    - Settings
    - Fullscreen
    - 'New project' wizard
    - Tag system for notes and sheets
    - Note pad in the Write page
    - Dynamic layout for all displays
    - Accessible for screen readers
    - French translation
    Other:
    - Flatpak manifest




